mountain justice is a 1937 american drama film directed by michael curtiz and starring george brent , nancy cooper and george brent . the film stars george brent , george brent , nils asther , george brent , nils asther , george brent , nils asther , and george brent . the film was released by warner bros. on september 23 , 1937 . the film was released on may 15 , 1937 , by paramount pictures .